      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "## Chandroid Enhanced Animations\n\n#### Varied Walking animations\n- [x] **walking towards player**: more feminine, jovial (wrists up, arms out, hips turn, vertically bouncy)\n- [x] **walking towards object**: strut, purposeful\n- [x] **walking to location**: current anim, normal\n\n#### Fidget Animations\n- [x] looking around\n- [x] stretching\n- [x] rolling her shoulders\n- [x] checking her nails\n- [x] shifting her weight\n- [x] checking herself out (turning her hips)\n- [x] holding palm up, moving thumb around\n- [x] touching her hair\n---\n\n\n#### Dog Fear\n- [x] jitters when near dog house or dog\n- [x] cowers if player brings held dog too close\n\n- [x] solve movement + interaction + fidgeting + reaction priority hierarchy\n---\n\n- [x] varied walking sfx\n- [x] eye fixation jitters",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 680,
      "x": 27160,
      "y": 260
    },
    {
      "height": 360,
      "id": "ecec7f0e77eae420",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "[[Science Nerd]] pulls a knife on [[Chandroid]] at the last second, camera shows it behind his back, then he lunges, drives the knife towards her chest, but it clinks and bends, making her breasts jiggle. Camera pans up from her chest onto her looking down, then blinking, then looking forward, angry.\n\n[[Science Nerd]] then cowers in the corner, powerless and  irrelevant.\n[[Chandroid]] turns back to the player. Start ending sequence.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 660,
      "x": 30110,
      "y": -780
    },
