      "text": "mountains experiement lobby\n\n- [ ] skull shaped desk area\n\t- [ ] desks\n\t\t- [ ] monitors (lore notes)\n- [ ] floor littered with coffee cups and caffeine pills (also briefly in previous rooms)\n- [ ] drawings of strange creatures plastered on walls",
