    {
      "height": 1800,
      "id": "1699ee7faeaaa3cd",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "### Lore (after NPCs & bosses)\nSewer 2\n- [ ] pipe system\n\t- why (transport batteries, metal balls placeholder for testing)\n\t- how (drilling and fitting)\n- nephew Raymond finally accepted on team\n- post-peace-award wishlist\n- retirement plan after working under [[Science Nerd]]\n\nToni wants a stable and easy job, which is why he gave up on being a pilot. He is a technician, an engineer.\n\nSewer 4\n- [ ] chandroid battery\n\t- Not Rosie's. It's an older model battery. It takes a lot of power to run a transport system, so a Chandroid battery is ideal.\n\nJungle Discotech\n- [ ] people have to wait their turn to get up on the pedestal and dance\n\nMountains library\n- [ ] Immanuel is attempting to map ancient mystic babble onto quantum equations, hoping he will be able to create a supernatural portal\n\nMountains experiement lobby\n- [ ] Immanuel is haunted by nightmares of burning flesh and strange creatures. He fears some great invasion or disaster is upon us, confirmed by his studies of the ancients.\n- [ ] Immanuel took hallucinagenic drugs, and consequently saw shadows of these creatures, even spoke to them. They reassured him that the end could be avoided if he came to their realm.\n- [ ] \"Drug notes\" an active bubble sort list of hallucinogens ranked by potency.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 520,
      "x": 27960,
      "y": 320
    },
    {
      "height": 1800,
      "id": "73f709e04568d128",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "### NPCs (after environments)\n- [ ] generic shopkeep NPC design\n\t- [ ] upright standing animation\n\t- [ ] blush on 1st girl\n\t- [ ] wave + grin animation for interactions\n\t- [ ] big cute hair (blender)\n- [ ] pitstop NPCs\n\t- [ ] clerk\n\t\t- [ ] sketch w/ primary colors and mood\n\t\t- [ ] model\n\t\t- [ ] animation\n\t- [ ] resident in chair?\n\t\t- [ ] sketch w/ primary colors and mood\n\t\t- [ ] model\n\t\t- [ ] animation\n- [ ] supermarket\n\t- [ ] clerk\n\t- [ ] shopper\n- [ ] beach\n\t- [ ] girls playing with beach ball (sprocketable)\n- [ ] beach changing room interior\n\t- [ ] changing girl (shocked/covers herself when drop down, underwear)\n\t- [ ] makeup girl (bikini)\n\t- [ ] showering girl (bubbles)\n\t- [ ] nursing girl (one breast out for baby)\n- [ ] discotech lobby\n\t- [ ] hostess\n- [ ] discotech\n\t- [ ] bird girl\n\t- [ ] zebra girl\n\t- [ ] giraffe girl\n\t- [ ] monkey girl\n\t- [ ] lioness\n\t\t- [ ] stands with arms crossed, looking ahead\n\t\t- [ ] shakes head \"no\" when interacted with\n\t\t\t- [ ] when all batteries are turned on, looks at player smiling\n\t\t\t- [ ] steps aside when interacted with, revealing door to dressing room\n- [ ] discotech dressing room\n\t- [ ] meercat girl\n\t- [ ] warthog girl",
