      "text": "## Features\n\n- [ ] [[Action Log]] #Feature\n- [ ] zoom button #Feature\n- [ ] SoundArea component #Feature\n- [ ] [[Companion Interact Menu]] #Feature\n- [ ] [[Chandroid Snatcher]] #Feature\n- [ ] [[Puzzle Stats Console]] #Feature\n- [ ] \"adjust brightness until left image is barely visible\" #Feature\n- [ ] floating icons for blueprints? #Feature\n- [ ] make rewire work if you select target first #Feature\n- [ ] opacity for chandroid silohuette setting #Feature\n- [ ] vizualize pathfinding? #Feature\n- [ ] [[Save point love seats]] #Feature\n\n\n## Conveyance\n\n- [ ] lift intro companion rewire pad should not afford pressing (surround by powered cage? phone booth?) #Conveyance\n- [ ] when no accessories, show \"No accessories unlocked!\" in character customizer #Conveyance\n- [ ] indication before characters speak to you #Conveyance\n- [ ] upgrade info box indication animation #Conveyance\n- [ ] indication on doors to tell you if they're locked #Conveyance\n- [ ] notification in [[Cosplay Crafter]] for \"change appearance in pause menu\" after first crafted item, and maybe a ? button that will explain things #Conveyance\n\n\n## Characters\n\n- [ ] [[Wheelchair Elder]] #Character\n- [ ] [[Menally Ill Chandroid]] #Character\n- [ ] tomoko-style ping pong addict #Character\n- [ ] [[Starcrossed Cop and Robber]] #Character\n- [ ] [[MP3 Dealer]] #Character\n- [ ] botanist? #Character\n- [ ] [[Construction Worker w Chandroid]] #Character\n- [ ] Venom A. \"Adrenaline\" Momentum (his real name is Vince) #Character\n- [ ] impatient customer #Character\n- [ ] kid staring through shop window #Character\n\n\n## Bugs\n\n- [ ] fear sfx lingers if recall device is used without consoling chandroid #Bug\n- [ ] force field shader: depth outline appearing when field is open #Bug\n- [ ] inventory screen icons stretched? #Bug\n- [ ] NoLandCheckpoint doesn't play correct walk sfx #Bug\n\n\n## Details\n\n- [ ] Add tubes around the city #Detail\n- [ ] paintings/decor art #Detail\n- [ ] bathroom scale joke #Detail\n- [ ] animated reactions when chandroid is commanded to the shower or bed #Detail\n- [ ] have bananas flow to edge of water during bridge lower #Detail\n- [ ] monorail cart #Detail\n- [ ] fan #Detail\n- [ ] balconies #Detail\n- [ ] gene's gadget gallery full texture #Detail\n- [ ] more chandroid animations #Detail\n\t- [ ] more character\n\t- [ ] idle animations\n\t- [ ] step on button animation\n\t- [ ] etc\n- [ ] drinkable cup of coffee #Detail\n- [ ] Shop shelf items #Detail\n\t- [ ] dog walkers\n\t- [ ] cell phones\n\t- [ ] chargers\n\t- [ ] anti-gravity attachment\n\t- [ ] folding wall table\n\t- [ ] litter zapper\n\t- [ ] placeable indoor conveyor belt\n\t- [ ] hovering monkey bars for kids\n\t- [ ] auto-watering garden apparatus\n\t- [ ] bass boost lazyboy chair\n- [ ] Carnivorous plants #Detail\n- [ ] Improve mall elevator aesthetics #Detail\n- [ ] make vending machine spit out soda cans #Detail\n- [ ] create console for showing battery requirements, statistics #Detail\n- [ ] add buildings to rooftop scene? #Detail\n- [ ] add water to bottom of drained canal #Detail\n- [ ] add camera decoration to tunnels #Detail\n- [ ] puzzle idea: in school science fair, enter and solve potato battery #Detail\n- [ ] add decals to boxes in car guy's room #Detail\n- [ ] AI art character portraits? #Detail\n- [ ] cars and boats and planes #Detail\n- [ ] cat paws neko terminal in maidbot factory #Detail\n\n\n## Effects\n\n- [ ] chandroid getting chills when approaching doghouse? (Bool idle anim)\n- [ ] transistors in batteries get up and walk around before settling back down (maximum one per puzzle)\n- [ ] chibi chandroid running around in a little glass box in controller config in main menu\n\n\n## Clothing-Male\n\n- [ ] hipster hairstyle with shaved parts\n- [ ] spiky asian hairstyle\n- [ ] baseball cap - 4 designs\n\t- [ ] w/ fuzzy hair & clean hair\n- [ ] 4 futuristic headgears\n- [ ] 6 eye types\n- [ ] 4 shirts\n- [ ] 4 pants\n-