      "text": "Bonus:\n- [ ] UI\n\t- [x] fabric names\n\t\t- [x] pastel gradient?\n\t- [ ] coyote time for scanner & rewire\n\t- [ ] player fall sfx\n- [x] visual indicator of non-interactible terminal\n- [ ] transition polish\n\t- [x] disable light bridge audio for a few frames at start\n\t- [ ] transition thumbnails\n\t- [ ] add door opening + sound for tram\n- [ ] highway entrance\n\t- [ ] arch above\n\t- [ ] floor/prop decorations\n- [x] terminal screen redesign\n- [ ] home interior photo models: remove physics and shoulder upgrade\n- [ ] companion\n\t- [ ] chandroid footsteps change depending on speed\n\t- [ ] kiss animation for interacting with chandroid\n- [ ] dragon boss chamber\n\t- [ ] fix interrogation scene\n\t- [ ] fix cutscene timings w/o dialogue\n\t- [ ] add drained batteries to corners\n- [x] replace lore\n\t- [x] bridge\n\t- [x] factory\n\t- [x] liftintro2\n\t- [x] dog intro\n\t- [x] mall exterior\n\t- [x] mall interior\n\t- [x] dragon chamber\n\t- [x] playground\n\t- [x] shop\n\t- [x] marketplace\n- [ ] sky reddens from highway 2\n- [ ] sprinkler in highway 1\n- [ ] coyote time for jump (a split second)\n- [x] bug: player shoots to bottom when on edge of surface\n- [ ] rumble\n- [ ] zoom feature\n- [x] scene transition sfx\n\t- [x] walking on different surfaces (sfx selected per door)\n\t- [x] tactile, low-frequency \"poom\"\n\t\t- [x] player needs a hard cutoff knowing they've definitely initiated a scene transition\n- [ ] glyphs and icons for tutorials",
