      },
      "text": "- [ ] day/night variation\n\t- [x] solve contradiction\n- [x] arachnae kidnaps [[Chandroid]]\n- [x] tentacle catch\n- [x] confronting [[Science Nerd]] cutscene\n- [x] finding the battery\n- [x] island stranded\n- [ ] changing room\n- [x] [[Chandroid]] interaction: wave becomes kiss over time\n- [ ] hug chanthro\n- [ ] experiment lobby\n- [ ] big snake\n- [ ] credits\n\t- [ ] \"loading up digital album: 3-20XX\"\n\t- [ ] screenshots of fun moments across the game\n- [x] final scene (putting new battery, kiss behind curtain)\n\t- [ ] [[Chandroid]] wearing pajama pants and hairbun\n- [x] something more post credits scene ([[Science Nerd]] weeping over his book, loading up a garbage truck w/ [[Sci-Fi Nerd]], zoom on ominous face cover)\n\t- [ ] player respawns at new house, the original apartment is empty, and all their furniture is at the new house\n\t\t- [ ] flamingo in the backyard, etc\n\t\t- [ ] lexie & george moved next door\n\t\t\t- [ ] lexie hanging out outside",
