      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "construction area\ncliffside tower construction\nconstruction site visuals can be very loose, very unfinished-looking (space is not intended for use yet)\n- [ ] yellow scaffold flooring\n- [ ] blue/white I-beams for frames\n- [ ] rock wall behind\n- [ ] unfinished stairs\n- [ ] big battery\n\t- [ ] chrome seam wall panel\n\t- [ ] circular sprite contact points (alternating green/yellow rings)\n- [ ] open air on most walls\n- [ ] codec\n\t- [ ] move to scene\n\t- [ ] face",
