      "id": "40bd0bd351569af7",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "uptown\n- [ ] city walls\n\t- [ ] bg buildings\n\t- [ ] mono rail\n- [ ] stairs\n- [ ] sprocketable plastic piece\n\t- [ ] catch tabs\n\t- [ ] floor rails\n- [ ] alley has dumpster with air freshener can\n- [ ] transport to subway\n\t- [ ] tunnel under wall\n\t- [ ] art deco\n- [ ] elevator mechanism to get back to apartments\n- [ ] \"love shop\" just outside discotech to the east?\n\t- [ ] flowers\n\t- [ ] jewelry\n\t- [ ] electronics\n- [ ] transport to mountains\n\t- [ ] mountain clearly visible in bg\n\t- [ ] tram logo\n- [ ] wires/pipes/clotheslines going across space\n- [ ] internet",
